    <Label name="lblClientAbout" id="447fa84c-e8c5-4f7b-9a84-dd54c15a0d80">
        <caption>In order to spawn Slaves on remote workstations, a Web Test Client application must first be running on that workstation (these Web Test Clients can only be run as thin clients).  If the Slave(s) are to run as thin clients, then you must enter the Application Server's Port number.  If the Slave(s) are to run as standard clients, then you must enter the file path of the JADE binaries and the path and file name of the JADE Initialization file.</caption>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
        <parent name="shtClientSlaves"/>
        <parentBottomOffset>204</parentBottomOffset>
        <parentRightOffset>5</parentRightOffset>
